​
The Boca Blues Festival is a brand that will host its debut annual Blues Festival at the Sunset Cove Amphitheater 20405 Amphitheater Circle Boca Raton, FL 33498 in 2024.
​
A unique 2 day music festival experience combining the love of nothing but the Blues on stage along with delicious foods, beer & full liquor bars and an amazing weekend to remember with friends and family. 10 bands on stage with professional sound and lighting.
​
Lattiude-88, Inc. also produces the Vero Beach, FL Blues Festival and multiple art and cultural events around Florida.
